snippet.title: Dawn of the Tiberium Age v1.10.0 (AKA build 1.10) trailer
snippet.description:
For some reason YouTube fails to play this video nowadays, so I re-uploaded it: https://youtu.be/hDMOuC04Jfo

This is my second trailer for my mod; Dawn of the Tiberium Age. As you can see, this mod fully converts Tiberian Sun into C&C1 it also introduces the enhanced mode, which has some extra features in addition you already know from C&C1.
